Package my.uum

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    App
    This class is used to connect to the database and run the Telegram bot API and register bot.
    dbConnection
    This class is contains a lot of sql function for telegram bot interaction.
    golferData
    This class is to set and get the data of the students (golfer id, golfer name, golfer handicap, golfer telegram id).
    ManageGolfer
    This class is to manage (create, read, update, delete) the records of the golfer table in the database.
    ManageHole
    This class is to manage (create, read, update, delete) the records of the hole table in the database.
    ManageTournament
    This class is to manage (create, read, update, delete) the records of the tournament table in the database.
    telegramBot
    This class is the main structure of STIW3054_A202_GoalDiggers_bot and it will receive the input through Telegram Bots and return back the result.
